  <url type="homepage">https://midterm.app</url>
  <url type="help">https://reddit.com/r/MidtermApp</url>
  <description>
    <p>Midterm is a note-taking with study tools to help you memorize your materials easier. It allows you to write notes, create quizzes and make interactive flashcards.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Write notes with quizzes for studying (cloze deletion, image occlusion inspired from Anki).</li>
      <li>Sync notes with your phone and/or tablet.</li>
      <li>Dark mode.</li>
      <li>Powerful visual editor.</li>
      <li>Keep track of notes to study before exams.</li>
      <li>Collaborate and study with your friends.</li>
      <li>Support nested folders.</li>
      <li>Study offline (offline accessible).</li>
      <li>and many more.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
